Add meat and vegetables to slow cooker. Top with Simmer Sauce; cover. Cook on LOW 8 to 10 hours (or on HIGH 4 to 6 hours). 15 min before serving, cook noodles as directed on package; omitting salt. Meanwhile stir Finishing Sauce into slow cooker. Remove 1 cup liquid with ladle from slow cooker into medium bowl. Cool until noodles are done cooking. Stir sour cream into cooled liquid in bowl; return to slow cooker. Serve over hot cooked noodles.